        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last updated: February 14, 2026</p>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Introduction</h2>
            <p>Welcome to Lox Player. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring you have a positive experience while using our app. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use Lox Player.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
            <p><strong>Lox Player is designed with privacy in mind.</strong> We do not collect, store, or transmit any of your personal information or media content. All your files remain on your device and are never uploaded to our servers or any third-party services.</p>
            <p>The only data that may be collected includes:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Anonymous Usage Statistics:</strong> We may collect anonymous, aggregated data about app usage to improve performance and user experience</li>
                <li><strong>Crash Reports:</strong> If the app crashes, anonymous crash reports may be sent to help us fix bugs</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Permissions</h2>
            <p>Lox Player requires certain permissions to function properly:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Storage Permission:</strong> Used to access and play your local media files (videos and audio)</li>
                <li><strong>Internet Permission:</strong> Used to stream online content and check for app updates</li>
            </ul>
            <p>These permissions are used solely for the app's core functionality and are never used to collect or transmit your personal data.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Data Storage and Security</h2>
            <p>All your media files and preferences remain stored locally on your device. We implement industry-standard security measures to protect the app from unauthorized access. Since we don't collect your data, there's no risk of your personal information being exposed in a data breach.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
            <p>Lox Player may use the following third-party services:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Google Play Services:</strong> For app distribution and updates (Android only)</li>
                <li><strong>Content Providers:</strong> When streaming online content, you interact directly with third-party content providers. Their privacy policies apply to such interactions</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We do not use any third-party analytics or advertising services that track your activity within the app.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p>Lox Player does not knowingly collect any personal information from children under the age of 13. If you believe we have inadvertently collected such information, please contact us immediately.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by updating the "Last Updated" date at the top of this policy. Your continued use of Lox Player after any modifications constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Your Rights</h2>
            <p>Since Lox Player does not collect or store your personal data on our servers, there is no data for us to modify, delete, or provide to you. You have complete control over your media files as they remain on your device.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
